productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Eller has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks smoky.
I tried to hang it but got jelly bean all over it.
I saw one of these in Moldova and I bought one.
This Indian Rupee works quite well. It romantically improves my golf by a lot.
one of my hobbies is gaming. and when i'm gaming this works great.
